      "message": "Nice catch! My original thought was wrong. I thought it needs to first call NewQueryIterator and then call startQueryIterator. But this would cause the itemCh be blocked forever if the `Next()` is called by accidentally before `startQueryIterator()`.  \n\nSo no need a separate initialization function. I\u0027m going to add a TODO and will change on it in the following CL.",
